Category.Name: Root

Category.Name: System
Category.ToolTip: Category that contains items that belong to the system module of the transport layer.

StringReg.Name: TLVendorName
StringReg.ToolTip: Indicates the name of the transport layer vendor.
StringReg.Description: This is a read only element. It is a string that indicates the name of the transport layer vendor.

StringReg.Name: TLModelName
StringReg.ToolTip: Indicates the name of the transport layer Model.
StringReg.Description: This is a read only element. It is a string that indicates the name of the transport layer Model to distinguish different kinds of GenTL Producer implementations from one vendor.

StringReg.Name: TLID
StringReg.ToolTip: Indicates the ID of the transport layer.
StringReg.Description: This is a read only element. It is a string that indicates the ID of the transport layer.

StringReg.Name: TLVersion

StringReg.Description: This is a read only element. It is a string that indicates a vendor specific version string for this transport layer.

StringReg.Name: TLPath

IntReg.Name: InterfaceSelector_CtrlValue
IntReg.ToolTip: Selector for the different GenTL Producer interfaces.
IntReg.Description: Selector for the different GenTL Producer interfaces. Selector for the different GenTL Producer interfaces. This interface list only changes on execution of InterfaceUpdateList. The selector is 0-based in order to match the index of the C interface.
